------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. SCOPE OF PROTECTION
------------------------------------------------------------------------

obfush is a SOURCE-CODE obfuscator. It does not, and is not intended to,
hide RUNTIME behavior. System calls, file writes, network connections,
and process executions performed by an obfuscated script remain fully
visible to host-based instrumentation (strace, eBPF, auditd, EDR).
The operator is responsible for understanding this distinction.

